<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 15px;          
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        .hero-section .text-content {
            max-width: 50%;
        }
        .hero-section img {
            height: 550px;
            width:500px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .hero-section h5 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section">
        <img src="/img/aboutUs.jpg" alt="Tea on mountain">
        <div class="text-content">
            <h1>At Recipe Blog, we're on a culinary journey with one main ingredient: you.</h1>
            <h5>Our mission is to create a vibrant, inclusive community where cooking enthusiasts from all walks of life come together to share, discover, and savor the joys of home cooking.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Add other content here -->

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
